  description: "multiprocessing __qualname__ equality cross-check table in mpextra83 namespace — wave 246 theme: multiprocessing Process __qualname__ and exception __qualname__ equality cross-checks; Process.__qualname__.__eq__('Process')==True (cross-check); AuthenticationError.__qualname__.__eq__('AuthenticationError')==True (cross-check); BufferTooShort.__qualname__.__eq__('BufferTooShort')==True (cross-check); TimeoutError.__qualname__.__eq__('TimeoutError')==True (cross-check); ProcessError.__module__.__eq__('multiprocessing.context')==True (cross-check); verified with Python 3.14.3"
